<p>For Futura, make sure you sync a bold instance. Youâ€™ll need it for titles and the TOC later on.</p>

<h4 id="clean-out-the-swatches-panel">Clean out the Swatches panel</h4>

<p>We want to remove all un-needed swatches from the Swatches panel. Remember that book sync is non-destructive. It only adds content across documents, it doesnâ€™t remove any. Thatâ€™s why this needs to be done at the outset.</p>

<p>Delete all unused colours. Letâ€™s add two colours to the panel.</p>

<figure>
    <img class="size100" alt="setup-colours" src="/images/indesign-books-pinocchio/setup-colours.jpg" />
<figcaption>
  We've added Pantone Cool Grey 10 in CMYK and Orange that's 60% magenta and 100% yellow.
