<p>Set up page numbering on the documents. There will be no page numbers on the cover document, obviously. We want lower case roman numerals for the Front Matter document, ie: i, ii, iii, iv, etcâ€¦ Thereâ€™ll be regular arabic numerals for the chapter files of the document. ie: 1, 2, 3, 4, etcâ€¦</p>

